# Iteration 11: Reliability harness DelayProxy accept loop

## Evidence
Reliability calibration artifact: `test_logs/reliability/20260520-084619`

Run id: `rel-20260520084623-r01`

Observed:
- `latency-proxy.log` showed `accept_loop_error` shortly after worker proxy startup.
- Worker proxies shut down with `connections=0`.
- Task dispatch remained `[PROBE_FAIL]`, invalidating the intended nodepool-to-worker latency path.

## Fix
Changed `DelayProxy._accept_loop` so `socket.timeout` continues the accept loop instead of being treated as fatal.

Added `scripts/reliability_harness_test.py::DelayProxyTests.test_proxy_accepts_connection_after_idle_timeout`.

